 Release Info:
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~

 In Tour de France 2015 you play a professional rider competing in the 
 "Grande Boucle". Immerse yourself in this supreme virtual challenge and 
 experience the high-octane adrenaline and thrills of the greatest 
 champions in the sport today! Select one of the official teams 
 participating in the Tour and embark on a fabulous Tour de France 2015 
 that will take you through Holland and the cobbled routes of Northern 
 France, to the summits of the mythical climbs and the legendary final 
 on the Champs-Elysees
